    <name>I-SIMPA</name>
    <summary>Room acoustics simulation software</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
            I-SIMPA is a graphical user interface (GUI) for room acoustics simulations.
            It allows users to model indoor sound propagation and analyze acoustic parameters.
        </p>
        <p>
            Features include:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>3D scene modeling and visualization</li>
            <li>Multiple calculation codes support (SPPS, TC, etc.)</li>
            <li>Acoustic materials database</li>
            <li>Sound source and receiver positioning</li>
            <li>Results analysis and visualization</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

    <launchable type="desktop-id">org.noise_planet.i-simpa.desktop</launchable>

